    "Still, there is a declining benefit soon after reaching these thresholds.",
    "It is, therefore, important to find the optimal scale to make both economic and environmental sustainability possible.After pre-training, models are fines-tuned or instructiontuned, whereby the model is tuned with small data to get some of the behaviors elicited.",
